features: 【Versatile Silicone Suction Phone Holder】 – This cutting-edge silicone double-sided phone holder features 41 suction cups, offering a unique solution to securely attach your phone to various smooth surfaces for activities like photography, video recording, chatting, or watching movies. Ditch the bulky tripod and effortlessly create social media content wherever you go.

【Reliable Suction Design】 – Equipped with 41 large independent suction cups, this silicone suction phone holder ensures a robust and dependable grip, minimizing concerns about accidental falls or drops during your photo or video sessions. With its versatile design, it eliminates the need for a traditional tripod, providing a flexible and convenient solution.

【Enhanced Stability with Suction Cups】 – The multitude of suction cups delivers enhanced stability, and the holder doesn't rely on magnets. Instead, it offers a reliable grip, ensuring your phone stays securely in place. This design accommodates phones, including the iPhone 15/14/13/13 series, and allows for the attachment of a magnetic ring to non-magnetic cases, enabling compatibility.

【Perfect for Content Creation】 – Whether you're an influencer, TikTok, Instagram, or YouTube creator, or simply someone who enjoys sharing content, the silicone suction phone holder is an ideal tool for capturing those memorable moments. It also makes for an excellent Christmas gift for friends and family.

【Easy Attachment and Removal】 – The silicone mount effortlessly adheres to various smooth surfaces, including vanity mirrors, glass windows, computer screens, refrigerators, tiles, and more. Compatible with a wide range of phone brands such as iPhone, Galaxy, Google, HTC, etc. If using non-magnetic regular phones or cases, the inclusion of a metal ring enhances the magnetic function.
